  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>POLY IMPULSE</strong> is a minimalist fast-paced movement FPS where you will have to shoot colorful polyhedrons to impulse yourself through the level. Accuracy is also very important so you will put your aim to a test with this game! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Shoot neon green icosahedron to impulse yourself and gain speed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805260/extras/20f0f628b1f7624ae0964b1638118182.poster.avif?t=1773845977\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805260/extras/20f0f628b1f7624ae0964b1638118182.webm?t=1773845977\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805260/extras/20f0f628b1f7624ae0964b1638118182.mp4?t=1773845977\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Speedrun the levels and compete with yourself and the global leaderboard to prove that you are the number one.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805260/extras/14c7c48cbe458c8411bf065c6d838169.poster.avif?t=1773845977\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805260/extras/14c7c48cbe458c8411bf065c6d838169.webm?t=1773845977\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805260/extras/14c7c48cbe458c8411bf065c6d838169.mp4?t=1773845977\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Different polyhedrons have different effects, shoot them and master their effects to get better ranks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805260/extras/eb63b24e2514ec2bceb53acf33c7d4a4.poster.avif?t=1773845977\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805260/extras/eb63b24e2514ec2bceb53acf33c7d4a4.webm?t=1773845977\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805260/extras/eb63b24e2514ec2bceb53acf33c7d4a4.mp4?t=1773845977\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>POLY IMPULSE</strong> is a minimalist fast-paced movement FPS where you will have to shoot colorful polyhedrons to impulse yourself through the level. Accuracy is also very important so you will put your aim to a test with this game! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Shoot neon green icosahedron to impulse yourself and gain speed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805260/extras/20f0f628b1f7624ae0964b1638118182.poster.avif?t=1773845977\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805260/extras/20f0f628b1f7624ae0964b1638118182.webm?t=1773845977\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805260/extras/20f0f628b1f7624ae0964b1638118182.mp4?t=1773845977\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Speedrun the levels and compete with yourself and the global leaderboard to prove that you are the number one.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805260/extras/14c7c48cbe458c8411bf065c6d838169.poster.avif?t=1773845977\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805260/extras/14c7c48cbe458c8411bf065c6d838169.webm?t=1773845977\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805260/extras/14c7c48cbe458c8411bf065c6d838169.mp4?t=1773845977\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Different polyhedrons have different effects, shoot them and master their effects to get better ranks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805260/extras/eb63b24e2514ec2bceb53acf33c7d4a4.poster.avif?t=1773845977\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805260/extras/eb63b24e2514ec2bceb53acf33c7d4a4.webm?t=1773845977\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805260/extras/eb63b24e2514ec2bceb53acf33c7d4a4.mp4?t=1773845977\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
