      "votes_up": 1,
      "playtime_at_review": 407,
      "review_text": "I got this on a whim that I'd find some enjoyment in it, but man that's an understatement. This game will humble you QUICK, but it's so amazing and really scratches an itch I didn't realize I had. Kovaaks was always fun/chill to do but this takes it to another level for me. Such a unique and fresh blend of movement/aim mechanics make this game so so fun to play. Really looking forward to completing the rest of the levels and grinding for better runs!!",
